data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in a gated community! Freshly painted light & bright throughout! Tons of room to grow-3,736 sq ft, 3 beds, 2.5 baths, office, game room + den & versatile room between guest beds. Recently remodeled kitchen showcases quartz countertops, shaker cabinets, large island & an open concept design, an ideal space for entertaining. Kitchen includes a breakfast area ideal for casual dining or enjoying morning coffee w a view. Private study upon entry, a dining room for formal gatherings & an open living area that seamlessly connects the spaces. All beds are down. Between guest bedrooms is a versatile area perfect for a second study, playroom, or gym. Upstairs a spacious game room, half bath & den await, den can easily be converted to a bedroom. The pool-sized backyard invites relaxation while observing the friendly ducks and turtles in the community lake. 3 AC zones for personalized comfort. Climate-controlled garage. New Roof June 23!
